<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Privacy Policy — CanadianPulse</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;background:#0a0a0b;color:#e8e8ee;min-height:100vh;padding:0;}
.header{background:rgba(10,10,11,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a30;padding:0 1.5rem;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.header-inner{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;height:56px;gap:1rem;}
.logo{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.4rem;color:#888896;text-decoration:none;}
.logo:hover{color:#e8e8ee;}
.back-btn{margin-left:auto;padding:0.4rem 1rem;background:transparent;border:1px solid #2a2a30;border-radius:20px;color:#888896;font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;}
.back-btn:hover{border-color:#555560;color:#e8e8ee;}
.page{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem 6rem;}
.page-title{font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
.page-meta{font-size:0.8rem;color:#555560;margin-bottom:3rem;padding-bottom:2rem;border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a30;}
h2{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem;color:#e8e8ee;}
p{font-size:0.925rem;line-height:1.8;color:#888896;margin-bottom:1rem;}
a{color:#e8354a;text-decoration:none;}
a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
ul{padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
ul li{font-size:0.925rem;line-height:1.8;color:#888896;margin-bottom:0.25rem;}
.highlight{background:#18181c;border:1px solid #2a2a30;border-radius:10px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.highlight p{margin:0;color:#e8e8ee;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">CanadianPulse</a>
    <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to Feed</a>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="page">
  <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="page-meta">Last updated: March 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; CanadianPulse</div>

  <div class="highlight">
    <p>The short version: We collect only what we need to run the platform. We never sell your data. We never share it with advertisers. Ever.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
  <p>CanadianPulse is a Canadian news aggregation platform. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information in accordance with Canada's <em>Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act</em> (PIPEDA).</p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect only the minimum information necessary to operate the Platform:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email address</strong> — collected when you create an account or subscribe to our newsletter</li>
    <li><strong>Username</strong> — chosen by you at registration, displayed publicly on your comments</li>
    <li><strong>Password</strong> — stored as a one-way cryptographic hash (we cannot read your password)</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — stories you save or like, comments you post (tied to your account)</li>
    <li><strong>Technical data</strong> — standard server logs including IP address and browser type, retained for up to 30 days for security purposes</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not collect your real name, phone number, location, or payment information.</p>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your information is used solely to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Create and manage your account</li>
    <li>Deliver the newsletter if you subscribed</li>
    <li>Display your comments and username on the Platform</li>
    <li>Remember your saved and liked stories across sessions</li>
    <li>Investigate abuse or security incidents if they arise</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. What We Do Not Do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We do not sell your personal information to anyone</li>
    <li>We do not share your data with advertisers or data brokers</li>
    <li>We do not run behavioural advertising or tracking pixels</li>
    <li>We do not use your data to train AI models</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
  <p>Your data is stored in a secured PostgreSQL database hosted on Supabase infrastructure in accordance with their security standards. Passwords are hashed using bcrypt and are never stored in plain text. We use HTTPS for all data transmission.</p>
  <p>While we take reasonable precautions, no system is 100% secure. In the event of a breach that puts your information at risk, we will notify you promptly as required by PIPEDA.</p>

  <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain your account data for as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, your personal information will be removed within 30 days. Comments you posted may be anonymized rather than deleted to preserve conversation context.</p>

  <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use a small number of third-party services to operate the Platform:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — database hosting</li>
    <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — font delivery (no personal data shared)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any other third-party tracking tools.</p>

  <h2>8. Your Rights Under PIPEDA</h2>
  <p>As a Canadian resident, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
    <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent and request deletion of your account and data</li>
    <li>File a complaint with the Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@canadianpulse.ca">privacy@canadianpulse.ca</a></p>

  <h2>9. Cookies</h2>
  <p>CanadianPulse does not use tracking cookies. We use browser localStorage solely to keep you logged in between sessions. No data stored locally is shared with any third party.</p>

  <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>CanadianPulse is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with their information, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>

  <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy as the Platform evolves. We will update the "Last updated" date at the top and, for material changes, notify registered users by email.</p>

  <h2>12. Contact</h2>
  <p>Privacy questions or requests: <a href="mailto:privacy@canadianpulse.ca">privacy@canadianpulse.ca</a></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
